--- !u!114 &147188275
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 147188273}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e939807b669dc4e7f8275d4d57f9837f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC
  npcName: Kallias
  relationshipGain: 5
  dialogueLow: I would choose your next words carefully. I have a long memory and
    a longer reach.
  dialogueNeutral: Everything in this city moves through the Agora. And everything
    in the Agora moves through me.
  dialogueFriendly: You are not as foolish as you look. That is a compliment, in
    case you were wondering.
  dialogueClose: I will tell you something I tell very few people. The city rewards
    those who know which doors to knock on. Knock on mine.
  dialogueFestivalGeneric: Festivals are excellent for business. Everyone is generous
    when the gods are watching.
  dialogueCityDionysia: 
  dialogueThargelia: 
  dialoguePanathenaia: I have arranged the seating for the official delegation. Naturally
    I kept the best positions for myself.
  dialogueHephaestia: 
  dialogueThesmophoria: 
  dialoguePyanopsia: 
  dialogueLenaia: Even in winter people need someone to smooth the way. That someone
    is me.
  dialogueHaloa: 
  interactionRadius: 0.5
  timeCostMinutes: 30
  conversationCooldownSeconds: 10
  promptUI: {fileID: 1135092676}
  romancePromptUI: {fileID: 0}
  loanPromptUI: {fileID: 1595425219}
