--- !u!114 &272387191
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 272387189}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e939807b669dc4e7f8275d4d57f9837f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC
  npcName: Xanthos
  relationshipGain: 5
  dialogueLow: I have no time for men who cannot keep up.
  dialogueNeutral: The Panathenaia is closer than people think. I am ready. The question
    is whether Athens is ready to watch.
  dialogueFriendly: You have something about you. Not strength exactly. Determination,
    maybe. I respect that more than strength anyway.
  dialogueClose: You are the kind of person I would want beside me if things went
    badly. That is the highest thing I know how to say.
  dialogueFestivalGeneric: Every festival is a chance to show Athens what its athletes
    are made of.
  dialogueCityDionysia: 
  dialogueThargelia: 
  dialoguePanathenaia: I competed in the footrace today. I won. Obviously. But the
    margin was closer than last year. That troubles me.
  dialogueHephaestia: The torch race is mine every year. No one has come close in
    three seasons.
  dialogueThesmophoria: 
  dialoguePyanopsia: 
  dialogueLenaia: 
  dialogueHaloa: 
  interactionRadius: 0.5
  timeCostMinutes: 30
  conversationCooldownSeconds: 10
  promptUI: {fileID: 55379218}
  romancePromptUI: {fileID: 0}
  loanPromptUI: {fileID: 0}
