--- !u!114 &757209004
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 757209002}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e939807b669dc4e7f8275d4d57f9837f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPC
  npcName: Phaedra
  relationshipGain: 5
  dialogueLow: Aphrodite sees the coldness in your heart. Do not expect her blessing.
  dialogueNeutral: The goddess watches all of Athens. Even those who do not think
    to look up.
  dialogueFriendly: You have a quality I do not often see in men who visit the temple.
    Sincerity, I think.
  dialogueClose: I have prayed for you. Do not ask me what I said. Some things belong
    to the goddess alone.
  dialogueFestivalGeneric: The goddess moves through the city on days like this.
    Can you not feel it?
  dialogueCityDionysia: Love and theatre have always been companions. Aphrodite smiles
    on this festival.
  dialogueThargelia: 
  dialoguePanathenaia: 
  dialogueHephaestia: 
  dialogueThesmophoria: I observe from a distance today. Some mysteries are not mine
    to enter. I respect that.
  dialoguePyanopsia: 
  dialogueLenaia: Winter theatre has a particular intimacy. The goddess appreciates
    what is offered in the cold.
  dialogueHaloa: 
  interactionRadius: 0.5
  timeCostMinutes: 30
  conversationCooldownSeconds: 10
  promptUI: {fileID: 1424777630}
  romancePromptUI: {fileID: 0}
  loanPromptUI: {fileID: 0}
